item.title: Written On The Scars Of Our Hearts
item.media:title: Written On The Scars Of Our Hearts
item.media:description:
A writer named JerseyBittons on AO3 contacted me about illustrating one of her Undertale fanfictions. I...rarely read Sans/Reader stories, they're typically not my thing, but I've been reading hers and it's actually pretty good. Basis of the story so far (because the story's still really new) is that a young girl running away from her life on the Surface accidentally hits Sans with her car. Instead of leaving him to die, like many people might have, she endeavors to save his life by finding his family, thus being introduced to all of our much beloved characters. JerseyBittons warned me that this story may contain some more mature content later on, so fair warning, and it does have some swearing. So, just a heads up.

STORY-----------> archiveofourown.org/works/1749…

I am planning on doing profiles like this for the comic as new main characters appear. The story is going to have 3 main characters total, plus one other character I really wanna do a profile for.

item.title: Good Boy Sketch
item.media:title: Good Boy Sketch
item.media:description:
One of the Papyrus' mentioned in TOLB (my fanfiction) and here he is in his AU before it got destroyed and he ended up in the Omega timeline with the other Swaps.

He is referred to as 'Good Boy' because he's generally the quietest, calmest, most polite and considerate Swap Papyrus in the bunch, plus he quit smoking BEFORE Frisk/Chara's Resets (because i don't like smoking )

I have sketched a 33 page comic about Good Boy but I didn't know he was 'Good Boy' back in October when I drew it. There is a bit more about him now that has sort of appeared since his mention in TOLB... i also decided that TO BE FAIR TO ALL THE SORIELS OUT THERE.... in his AU, being that it is a SWAP universe, the SWAP SORIEL SHOULD BE ASGYRUS/PAPGORE.... so he ends up being totes gay for the goat papa ^_^ (i really love the Swap Soriel with Sans BECAUSE I'M A HUGE SORIEL SHIPPER X3 but in all honesty because it's a Swap universe, that's like pairing papyrus up with Asgore anyway sooo...thought I'd be fair and have it this way ahaha)

Good Boy is quite depressed every time I draw him tbh... he's REALLY SERIOUS about EVERYTHING. And he's 'given up' like Undertale Sans did

I thought I'd try Sans out with actual SEPARATED teeth... it's a weird effect... Sans being able to...open...his...mouth... What with that slightly jutting out jaw too he just makes me think of Horror!Sans the way his creator draw him (quite ape-jawed). OH YEAH and for once I wanted to draw a Swap Sans that was SERIOUS and NORMAL not HIGH ON SUGAR

THIS WILL GO INTO MY SCRAPS EVENTUALLY.... but I will redraw this digitally using this as a base I think.

Undertale by Toby Fox
Underswap belongs to 'The Community'
